skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hong kong travel
des:
The purpose of the skill is to show you how to go to the places in Hong Kong.

No prerequisites are required.

You can say "Alexa ask Hong Kong Travel, give me the IFC mall" and the skill will show you the near MTR exit such as "Blue Line Central MTR Station Exit A"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
